# Walkthrough: Autonomous Ticket Triage and Routing System

## Summary

Built a complete end-to-end Python system for automatic ticket triage using RAG and LLMs. The project comprises **24 source files** across **7 packages**, running inside a Python virtual environment with all dependencies installed.

## Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[GitHub GraphQL API] --> B[Data Ingestion]
    B --> C[Preprocessing<br/>Regex + spaCy]
    C --> D[Embedding<br/>BAAI/bge-large-en]
    D --> E[ChromaDB<br/>Vector Store]
    
    F[User Ticket] --> G[Pipeline]
    G --> C2[Preprocess]
    C2 --> H[Hybrid Retrieval]
    E --> H
    H --> I[Cross-Encoder<br/>Reranking]
    I --> J[Classification<br/>Gemini]
    I --> K[RAG Generation<br/>Gemini]
    J --> L[FastAPI<br/>Response]
    K --> L
```

